{
  "texts": [
    "The data was assembled from the INCF Infrastructure Catalog, FAIRsharing, the SciCrunch Registry (Subash et al., 2023) and examination of repository websites.",
    "As shown in Figure 3, multiple repositories and infrastructures are connected via these standards.",
    "For example, the Brain Imaging Data Structure (BIDS; Gorgolewski et al., 2016) links 10 different repositories and computational platforms.",
    "The success of BIDS has led to extensions of BIDS for other modalities through a formal governance process (Governance, n.d.).",
    "The adoption of these BIDS-based standards starts to create a degree of interoperability across data types."
  ]
}